---
import storyImage from "../assets/story-girl.png";
---

<section class="bg-[#FAF7F2] py-20 sm:py-28">
  <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl items-center gap-14 px-5 sm:px-6 lg:grid-cols-[1.08fr_0.92fr] lg:gap-16">
    <img
      src={storyImage.src}
      alt="Priya, a Children First student"
      class="h-[520px] w-full rounded-[2rem] object-cover sm:h-[700px] lg:rounded-[3rem]"
    />

    <div>
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-[#D97706] sm:text-sm">
        Featured Story
      </p>

      <h2 class="mt-6 text-5xl font-bold leading-tight text-[#1F2937] sm:text-6xl md:text-8xl">
        Meet Priya
      </h2>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
        Priya arrived unsure if her voice belonged in the classroom. With steady learning support and a mentor who kept showing up, she began reading aloud, asking questions and trusting her own progress.
      </p>

      <p class="mt-8 max-w-xl text-lg leading-8 text-[#1F2937]/70 md:text-xl md:leading-9">
        Her story is not about one dramatic moment. It is about the quiet power of being seen, encouraged and given room to grow.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
